    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Allogeneic stem cell transplant recipient

          -  Recipient CMV seropositive

          -  Have transplant engraftment

          -  Able to swallow tablets

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  CMV organ disease

          -  HIV infection

          -  Use of other anti-CMV therapy post-transplant
      </textblock>
